## When to use this data source

Use `thousandeyes_dashboard_filter` when a saved dashboard filter already exists in ThousandEyes and you want Terraform to attach that filter to a dashboard by name.

This data source does an exact name match and returns the saved filter's `filter_id`. It does not manage the filter itself, and it is different from widget `filter` blocks inside `thousandeyes_dashboard`.

